Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I select 'Yes' radio button from contrast enhanced box in Page 03
And	I'm on Page 04 of Hip MRI
And I select 'Finding' radio button

When I select 'Coxarthrosis' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled

And 'Femur' checkbox is enabled
And 'Acetabulum' checkbox is enabled
And 'Chondropathy' checkbox is enabled

And 'Joint space narrowing' checkbox is enabled
And 'Articular effusion' checkbox is enabled
And 'Bone marrow edema' checkbox is enabled
And 'Subchondral edema' checkbox is enabled
And 'Osteophytes' checkbox is enabled
And 'Subchondral cysts/geodes' checkbox is enabled
And 'Ganglion' checkbox is enabled
And 'Subchondral sclerosis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Synovial cyst' checkbox is enabled

And 'Synovitis' checkbox is enabled // only when CM is selected from Page 03
And 'Paralabral cysts' checkbox is enabled
And 'Intraarticular loose-body' checkbox is enabled

And 'Low' radio button is enabled
And 'Moderate' radio button is enabled
And 'Pronounced' radio button is enabled

And 'Grade 1' radio button is enabled
And 'Grade 2' radio button is enabled
And 'Grade 3' radio button is enabled
And 'Grade 4' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Chondropathy' checkbox
Then 'Superficial' radio button is enabled
And 'Full cartilage thickness' radio button is enabled
And 'Focal' radio button is enabled
And 'Diffuse' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Ganglion' checkbox
Then 'Max. diameter' input field is enabled

When I select 'Synovial cyst' checkbox
Then 'Max. diameter' input field is enabled

When I select 'Synovial cyst' checkbox
Then 'Quantity > 1' checkbox is enabled
And 'Max. diameter' input field is enabled
